law.text:
As to each insurer making or having a deposit the commissioner shall keep a complete record thereof showing:
The particular assets so deposited;
The face value, if any, of any asset, and the value thereof as determined by the commissioner;
Date of deposit, and place thereof;
Assets withdrawn, date thereof, value of assets so withdrawn, and the name and address of any person to whom the assets were delivered; and
All other information as the commissioner deems necessary.
